{"tid":794450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞運] 港棒球隊昨操練投訴印尼違規攝錄不果 印尼練習時更被大會困起 今擊敗印尼奪港棒亞運史首勝","createTime":"2018-08-26T09:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T07:54:39.000Z","uid":9030,"like":161,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b71ed56640a15d41a29aba7f41c5b38e993881af","tid":794450,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"港棒球操練印尼攝錄　投訴不果誓挑戰不公爭首勝<br />\n<br />\n港隊明(今)天首戰對東道主印尼，訓練期間場內卻出現小插曲，印尼隊的日籍教練竟然在觀眾席上拍攝香港隊練習，區教練無奈說：「投訴過，但負責人竟然說沒有問題，我們真的沒方法了，但這樣絕對不公平，印尼練習時，我們就要困在更衣室。」主場之利？我相信這已經超越了主場之利的範疇。<br />\n<br />\n港隊操練備戰對印尼，印尼練習時港隊不准內進，但到港隊練習，印尼卻派員錄影，港隊立即投訴，大會卻說規矩臨時更改。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1790322/org/24436c9834dbd3092f7139d39d82084f.jpg/Jaz-frHO1fw3dZmOqXaWA9UhjZEStrRRvghlAb4IZQE?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1790322%2Forg%2F24436c9834dbd3092f7139d39d82084f.jpg%2FJaz-frHO1fw3dZmOqXaWA9UhjZEStrRRvghlAb4IZQE%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=daaff88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港隊今日一度落後下終反勝5-3。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/DuBYVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FDuBYVN.png&h=21aa0a9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e7f680a40bc96d73f22d5dfbfccb9406d373dc9","tid":794450,"uid":6799,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"奸有奸輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d424cd29175099e9f971e3fa8ea9ce2755ab35","tid":794450,"uid":5601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8ad7ff3bd6ebcae83a3e8315f358123fba1db9","tid":794450,"uid":8883,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"撈麵狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8b5ac21500fc5c665268a5ee6ba0aa5f6949a2","tid":794450,"uid":132587,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20140514/photo/0514-00282-014h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140514%2Fphoto%2F0514-00282-014h1.jpg&h=0de2141a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"877fdfb93b882519edfb9e84ddf35d1ef3148409","tid":794450,"uid":3454,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"印尼隊的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日籍</span>教練竟然在觀眾席上拍攝香港隊練習<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b85b001cc7163d52c262d1685e3447d7e1aabf","tid":794450,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"運動員精神何在"},{"pid":"a6442e50fd4f7d64e7aaff7229caa2f9f148daba","tid":794450,"uid":70800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"咁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86e4c78ef07eaf9386ac5b1401ea6b073e78c57","tid":794450,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"877fdfb93b882519edfb9e84ddf35d1ef3148409","tid":794450,"uid":3454,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"印尼隊的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日籍</span>教練竟然在觀眾席上拍攝香港隊練習<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb890e75afae1f6ffcf87ea28c4c528c369d1c9","tid":794450,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p